data.description: Move In Ready! Completely redone first floor includes upgraded kitchen with white shaker cabinets and a white quartz waterfall island.  The island hosts a built in beverage fridge. The kitchen overlooks your custom built in with floating shelves and customizable electric fireplace. There is hidden storage/playspace  under the staircase. Outside welcomes you to lots of open space with a built in firepit surrounded by lush landscaping. Upstairs you'll find 5 bedrooms 3 bathrooms. Laundry is upstairs with Maytag appliances. A/C replaced in 2022. Newer hot water heater. New impact front doors with privacy glass. EV charging installed in garage. Recessed lighting on first floor and master is color changing. Nautica Isles has lots of amenities all recently updated.
